<p>I'm not typically a fan of these types of open world games (read Assassin's Creed); but Ghost of Tsushima really resonates with me. It's my GOTY so far, at least on PS4 and would easily give it an 8 or a 9; where as I would have given TLOU 2 a solid 7. TLOU 2 is a beautiful game no doubt and I take no umbrage with it's story, it's just far too dour during this period in time at no fault of it's own; just bad timing.</p></section>
