<section class="text">
<p>I find the extreme views between GOT and LOU2 is what’s putting me off buying GOT. I loved LOU2 and am surprised by how much people can’t see it as okay, it has to be a 0/10 and in the same breath will say GOT is 10/10. It makes me think their view is invalid in this situation even if it shouldn’t. <br />Saying this I also struggled with Witcher 3 and bloodborne which I’m gutted about, although will give them both a retry on PS5 once the loading issues are sorted. They’re too too damn difficult!!</p></section>
